    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071380/extras/4e445e6ac75ca3ba82746ce5735209b4.avif?t=1765297722\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >当&quot;恶役大小姐&quot;决定洗心革面，谁说反派没有春天？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女士们先生们，准备好了吗？来体验一把从恶毒女配逆袭成为人生赢家的快感吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071380/extras/45e29e00754530e8d9fc8f103e8a6568.avif?t=1765297722\" width=600 height=131 /></span>艾米丽·哈特利，曾经的校园&quot;<strong>头号刺头</strong>&quot;，因为作天作地被家族发配到独居公寓。现在，你将接管这个麻烦精的人生，带领她完成从&quot;<strong>熊孩子</strong>&quot;到&quot;<strong>优秀毕业学生</strong>&quot;的华丽转身！相信我，这绝对比考试周通宵赶论文还要刺激！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071380/extras/3becde98a7a7d38064e7ece1b3680307.avif?t=1765297722\" width=600 height=131 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071380/extras/1861bf88f2db76be5d2a107166130167.avif?t=1765297722\" width=600 height=390 /></span>• 瑞安：表面王子暗地腹黑的未婚夫。谁说霸道总裁已经过时了？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 丹特：活在哥哥阴影下的运动健将。傲娇指数：★★★★★</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 吉尔伯特：自带阳光特效的开朗少年。笑容太灿烂请戴墨镜观看。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 艾格尼丝：原作女主，正义感爆棚。是敌是友，就看你的了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 爱丽丝：自封的&quot;艾米丽监督官&quot;。想甩开她？门都没有！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 妮娜：表里不一的千金小姐。深不可测，approach with caution！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071380/extras/931ed02550db700d1ddbedb363721efe.avif?t=1765297722\" width=600 height=131 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071380/extras/ff3e4a12aab441681244ba8d429bd557.poster.avif?t=1765297722\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071380/extras/ff3e4a12aab441681244ba8d429bd557.webm?t=1765297722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071380/extras/ff3e4a12aab441681244ba8d429bd557.mp4?t=1765297722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 打工乐趣多：当托尼学徒、书店职员、模特新秀、女仆咖啡厅店花，还是侦探助手？每份工作都有超可爱的小动画！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 才艺培养：绘画、话剧、网球、学习、舞蹈，样样精通，变身才艺美少女！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 社团活动：芭蕾、话剧、绘画、推理、网球，校园生活精彩纷呈！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 休闲时光：滑板酷girl、逛街败家、睡美容觉、打游戏开黑，放松方式任你选！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071380/extras/ef038e040fccee8960d735e64082252b.avif?t=1765297722\" width=600 height=131 /></span>• 多重身份养成：学霸、交际花、黑道头目、家族骄傲，你想当哪个就当哪个！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 复杂人际关系：用你的魅力（或者头脑）征服每一个人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 家族和解：把严肃老爸变成温柔奶爸，成就达成！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 独立生活：第一次煮面没有把厨房炸飞？恭喜，你已经成长了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071380/extras/1acbbe87a77a5eaf2cc0c7318b86fda2.avif?t=1765297722\" width=600 height=131 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071380/extras/b29efbfe3e71e20ce8a6533ff6b8e058.avif?t=1765297722\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 花神节：在点心王争霸赛上，用&quot;意外&quot;烧焦的小点心征服评委！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 夏日祭：挑战极限！看看能不能用一个纸网捞起整缸的金鱼！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 露营活动：在&quot;卡牌生存&quot;中用魔法召唤出空调和Wi-Fi！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 试胆大会：当鬼怪爱上我?!邂逅各路奇葩鬼怪,从痴情小倩到捣蛋剑士,谁说鬼就不能谈恋爱?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071380/extras/dd74cfe61807c5efbe8b84216fb2becd.avif?t=1765297722\" width=600 height=131 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>商业精英</strong>：成为哈特利集团的优秀继承人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>网球明星</strong>：在网球界创造传奇</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>艺术大师</strong>：成为备受瞩目的天才画家</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超级巨星</strong>：在演艺圈留下不朽传奇</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>王牌侦探</strong>：成为破解悬案的神探警花</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>幻影怪盗</strong>：成就来去无踪的盗贼传奇</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>江湖骗子</strong>：以高超骗术游走于灰色地带</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071380/extras/02cc94de88c78bd7b81b02ea88f4c94a.avif?t=1765297722\" width=600 height=131 /></span>• 让曾经讨厌你的同学变成你的迷弟迷妹！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 在各种校园活动中一鸣惊人，让所有人膜拜你的才华！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 成功开启每个角色的心锁，收获真挚友情或甜蜜爱情！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好了吗？来挑战&quot;从最讨厌变成最受欢迎&quot;的终极任务吧！记住，在这个游戏里，你就是主角，你就是传奇，你就是……最闪耀的那颗星！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PPPPPPS：游戏不保证能让你在现实生活中也实现180度大转变。如果有人告诉你玩了这个游戏就能继承家族企业还能包分配对象，请立即报警！</p>",
